<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-04-05T14:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1954-04-05T14:00:00-05:00" n="696" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d696">
                    <note rend="inline" type="source">751G.00/4–554: Telegram</note>
                    <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_DCD1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Dillon</hi></persName>)
                            <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Department of
                            State</gloss></hi></head>
                    <opener>
                        <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">top secret<lb/><gloss target="#t_niact1">niact</gloss></hi></seg>
                        <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1954-04-05T20:00:00+01:00">April 5, 1954—8
                            p.m.</date><lb/>[Received 2:26 p.m.]</dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>3729. Limit distribution. I delivered message <gloss target="#t_Deptel1">Deptel</gloss> 3482<note n="1" xml:id="d696fn1"><ref target="#d695"><hi rend="italic">Supra</hi></ref>.</note> to <persName corresp="#p_BG1">Bidault</persName> Monday evening.<note n="2" xml:id="d696fn2">Apr. 5.</note> He asked me to tell Secretary that he
                        personally could well understand position US Government and would pass on
                        your answer to <persName corresp="#p_LJ1">Laniel</persName>.</p>
                    <p>He asked me to say once more that unfortunately the time for formulating
                        coalitions has passed as the fate of Indochina will be decided in the next
                        ten days at Dien-Bien-Phu. As I left he said that even though French must
                        fight alone they would continue fighting and he prayed God they would be
                        successful.</p>
                    <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_DCD1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Dillon</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>